@{
    ViewBag.Title = "BasementDrainTileSystem";
}
      
<div id='main-content'>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
           <div class="col-xs-12" id="mycontent">
            <section id="basement-draintile">
                <h1>Basement Drain Tile System</h1>
                <p class="lead lead-lg">Basement seepage and standing water issues can be common in homes that do not have a draintile system in place to collect and remove residual rain water.  We have a system, that once installed, can solve the problem.</p>
                                  
                <div class='panels-wrapper'>
                    <div class='row panels'>
                        <div class='panel panel-big'>
                            <div class='panel-icon'>
                                <i class='fa-icon-tint icon'></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class='panel-body'>
                                <div class="container">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-sm-12">
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class='col-sm-2'>
                                                    <div class='circle-stats text-center'>
                                                        <div class='circle-stat-small'>
                                                            <div class='circle-stat-wrapper'>
                                                                <input class='hidden' data-fgcolor='#8dc153' data-readonly='true' data-stat='circle' data-thickness='0.2' type='text' value='20'>
                                                                <h4 class='percent text-center'>1</h4>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class='col-sm-10'>
                                                    <h5 class="title">We plan the system in advance, so that we know where to locate the new sump pump and discharge.
                                                    </h5>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <br />
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class='col-sm-2'>
                                                    <div class='circle-stats text-center'>
                                                        <div class='circle-stat-small'>
                                                            <div class='circle-stat-wrapper'>
                                                                <input class='hidden' data-fgcolor='#8dc153' data-readonly='true' data-stat='circle' data-thickness='0.2' type='text' value='40'>
                                                                <h4 class='percent text-center'>2</h4>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class='col-sm-10'>
                                                    <h5 class="title">We remove about 10-12” of the existing concrete floor around the INSIDE perimeter of the basement.  We call this the “breakout”.
                                                    </h5>
                                                    <p>
                                                        The concrete and soil removed will be hauled away.                                        
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <br />
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class='col-sm-2'>
                                                    <div class='circle-stats text-center'>
                                                        <div class='circle-stat-small'>
                                                            <div class='circle-stat-wrapper'>
                                                                <input class='hidden' data-fgcolor='#8dc153' data-readonly='true' data-stat='circle' data-thickness='0.2' type='text' value='60'>
                                                                <h4 class='percent text-center'>3</h4>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class='col-sm-10'>
                                                    <h5 class="title">Once the perimeter concrete is removed, we trench the perimeter such that we can install a 4” diameter perforated plastic draintile, that we surround with drainage stone.
                                                    </h5>
                                                    <p>
                                                        Our draintile includes a filter sock t prevent clogging in the future. 
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>
                                                        This drain tile is connected at both end to a plastic sump pit with cover. 
                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <br />
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class='col-sm-2'>
                                                    <div class='circle-stats text-center'>
                                                        <div class='circle-stat-small'>
                                                            <div class='circle-stat-wrapper'>
                                                                <input class='hidden' data-fgcolor='#8dc153' data-readonly='true' data-stat='circle' data-thickness='0.2' type='text' value='80'>
                                                                <h4 class='percent '>4</h4>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class='col-sm-10'>
                                                    <h5 class="title">Once the drain tile and stone is in place, we cover the trench with minimum 2” concrete that will be finished flush with the exiting basement floor slab.
                                                    </h5>
                                                    <p>
                                                        We use a durable 1060P or equivalent concrete mix. 
                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <br />
                                            <div class="row">
                                                <div class='col-sm-2'>
                                                    <div class='circle-stats text-center'>
                                                        <div class='circle-stat-small'>
                                                            <div class='circle-stat-wrapper'>
                                                                <input class='hidden text-center' data-fgcolor='#8dc153' data-readonly='true' data-stat='circle' data-thickness='0.2' type='text' value='100'>
                                                                <h4 class='percent '>5</h4>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class='col-sm-10'>
                                                    <h5>We now install the new sump pump, which will be sized to handle the linear footage drain tile system.
                                                    </h5>
                                                    <p>
                                                        We use high quality Zoeller sump pumps and check valves... a typical installation is 1/3HP. 
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>
                                                        Our electrician can install a dedicated circuit, if required.
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>The discharge for the sump pump location is installed, per our discussion with the client.</p>
                                                    <h4>Once completed, we haul away the spoils and sweep up our dust.
                                                    </h4>
                                                    <h4>These systems carry a life time warranty !!
                                                    </h4>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>  
            </section>
           </div>
        </div>
    </div>
        <div class='fade' id='scroll-to-top'>
            <i class='fa-icon-chevron-up'></i>
        </div>   
</div>



